             was indicted for that <rs id="t17980523-16-off79" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17980523-16-off79" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17980523-16-off79" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
